                "content": "# About this alerting dashboard\n\nThis dashboard includes several [panels with linked alert rules](https://grafana.com/docs/grafana/latest/alerting/alerting-rules/link-alert-rules-to-panels/). You can find these panels on the left side:\n\n- Random Single Serie\n\n- Random Multiple Series\n\n- Users & PageViews\n\n- Browser market share > 50%\n\nBelow is a list of useful alert examples available in Play.\n\n\n\n- [Example of multi-dimensional alerts on time series data](/alerting/grafana/multi-dimensional-alerts/view)\n\n- [Example of alerting on tabular data](/alerting/grafana/tabular-data/view)\n\n- [Example of dynamic thresholds](/alerting/grafana/dynamic-thresholds/view)\n\n- [Example of dynamic labels](/alerting/grafana/dynamic-label/view)\n\n\nThe panel below — Alerts linked to this dashboard — is an Alert list visualization. Learn more about this visualization on this [Play dashboard](/d/bdodlcyou483ke/alert-list).",
